library(ggthemes)
library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)


mtcars |> 
  select(mpg, wt) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = wt, y = mpg)) + 
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", formula = y ~ x, se = FALSE) + 
  theme_clean() +
  labs()
